    <section class="story-section">
        <div class="container story-container">
            <div class="story-content">
                <h2>From Humble Beginnings</h2>
                <p>FoodFrenzy was founded in 2025 by two friends, Saqlain and Talha, who shared a simple vision: to make quality food accessible to everyone, delivered quickly and conveniently.</p>
                <p>What started as a small kitchen serving local neighborhoods has grown into a trusted food delivery service operating in over 20 cities. Our commitment to quality, speed, and customer satisfaction remains at the heart of everything we do.</p>
                <p>Today, we partner with hundreds of local restaurants and chefs to bring you diverse culinary experiences right to your doorstep.</p>

                <div class="story-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">20+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Cities Served</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">100K+</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Happy Customers</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">98%</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">Satisfaction Rate</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="story-image">
                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559339352-11d035aa65de?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8NXx8cmVzdGF1cmFudCUyMGNoZWZ8ZW58MHx8MHx8fDA%3D&w=1000&q=80" alt="Chef Cooking">
