            </div>

            <div class="mission-content">
                <h2>Our Mission & Vision</h2>
                <p>At FoodFrenzy, our mission is simple: to connect people with the food they love through fast, reliable delivery.</p>
                <p>We envision a world where everyone has access to delicious, high-quality meals regardless of their location or schedule constraints.</p>

                <ul class="mission-points">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Quality First:</strong> We carefully vet all restaurant partners to ensure they meet our high standards for food quality and safety.
                        </div>
                    </li>
               
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        <div>
                            <strong>Innovation Driven:</strong> We continuously improve our technology and processes to enhance the customer experience.
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section class="values-section">
        <div class="container">
