                    <h3>Speed & Efficiency</h3>
                    <p>We understand that when you're hungry, every minute counts. Our streamlined processes ensure your food arrives hot and fresh in record time.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Quality & Care</h3>
                    <p>From ingredient selection to final delivery, we maintain the highest standards to ensure every meal meets your expectations.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Community Focus</h3>
                    <p>We believe in building strong relationships with our customers, restaurant partners, and the communities we serve.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Sustainability</h3>
                    <p>We're committed to eco-friendly practices, from sustainable packaging to optimizing delivery routes to reduce our environmental impact.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-gem"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Transparency</h3>
                    <p>We believe in open communication about our processes, pricing, and partnerships to build trust with our customers.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="value-card">
                    <div class="value-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3>Innovation</h3>
                    <p>We continuously explore new technologies and approaches to enhance the food delivery experience for everyone involved.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
